<h1><font color="#5C8526">Milestone : Algorithm for Problem 2(contd.)</font></h1>
<ul><li><h2>The FROM clause is changed to be the union of the locations of the attributes in the SELECT clause</h2></li>
<li><h2>The WHERE clause of the query has the attributes pointing to the correct location and a JOIN on the X attribute has to be added given that X --&gt; Y was the newly added functional dependency</h2></li>
<li><h2>A foreign key constraint must be added for the X attribute</h2></li>
